{
  "id": "6999bb4fe26831c3f1957657",
  "title": "2026/02/22",
  "created": 1771682642,
  "updated": 1776339124,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6999bb4fe26831c3f1957657",
      "text": "2026/02/22",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771682642,
      "updated": 1771682642
    },
    {
      "id": "6999c8b97838e3000000c727bd",
      "text": "第9週: [[日]]月火水木金土",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1771686071,
      "updated": 1771686071
    },
    {
      "id": "6999c8b97838e30000000764cf",
      "text": "2026年 14.52％経過",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1771686071,
      "updated": 1771686071
    },
    {
      "id": "6999bb6e00000000005dfb47",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771682670,
      "updated": 1771682670
    },
    {
      "id": "6999bb6f00000000005dfb48",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771682672,
      "updated": 1771682672
    },
    {
      "id": "6999bb5200000000005dfb44",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771682642,
      "updated": 1771682659
    },
    {
      "id": "6999bb6300000000005dfb46",
      "text": "\t漢方薬美味しくない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771682659,
      "updated": 1771682665
    },
    {
      "id": "6999c7050000000000a1dec9",
      "text": "\t 漢方を処方されていることを思い出しました。ありがとう。[hoshihara.icon]",
      "userId": "640b5ab62ffe46001b897bef",
      "created": 1771685637,
      "updated": 1771685648
    },
    {
      "id": "6999bb7400000000005dfb49",
      "text": "\t苦いならシンプルでいいんだけど、微妙に美味しい成分が混ざってるのがキモい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771682676,
      "updated": 1771682725
    },
    {
      "id": "6999bbb100000000005dfb4a",
      "text": "\t最初に甘くてほんのり香ばしい香りがしつつ後味が苦い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771682738,
      "updated": 1771682922
    },
    {
      "id": "6999bc7900000000005dfb4b",
      "text": "\t\tでもこれだけだと焦げたパンの感想と同じだな",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771682938,
      "updated": 1771682978
    },
    {
      "id": "699b11930000000000fbde07",
      "text": "\t\t当帰芍薬散をコカ・コーラで流し込むとイソジンと高麗人参を合成したようなエグい風味になる[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771770260,
      "updated": 1771794614
    },
    {
      "id": "6999bb6300000000005dfb45",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771682659,
      "updated": 1771682659
    },
    {
      "id": "6999c8c50000000000758c04",
      "text": "[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1771686084,
      "updated": 1771686085
    },
    {
      "id": "699a65050000000000d427da",
      "text": "　[善意しか送れないコミュニケーションツール]とはどんなものか",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1771726086,
      "updated": 1771726100
    },
    {
      "id": "699a65140000000000d427db",
      "text": "　　特定ワードやスタンプしか使えないとか",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1771726100,
      "updated": 1771726118
    },
    {
      "id": "699a904c000000000054f037",
      "text": "　　 こんな感じ？[suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1771737165,
      "updated": 1771737270
    },
    {
      "id": "699a9029000000000054f036",
      "text": "　　  [ええ腕時計してはりますなぁ]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1771737129,
      "updated": 1771737173
    },
    {
      "id": "699a901b000000000054f035",
      "text": "　　　 [にぎやかでよろしおすなぁ]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1771737115,
      "updated": 1771737175
    },
    {
      "id": "699a91760000000000f3bd8d",
      "text": "　　👍や❤が「やばい」並の多義語になりそう[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1771737463,
      "updated": 1771737488
    },
    {
      "id": "699ae358000000000027808a",
      "text": "　　京言葉が発展する[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771758425,
      "updated": 1771758426
    },
    {
      "id": "699a1f740000000000dfa045",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771708274,
      "updated": 1771708274
    },
    {
      "id": "699a1f740000000000dfa046",
      "text": "[taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771708274,
      "updated": 1771708276
    },
    {
      "id": "699a1f760000000000dfa047",
      "text": " 朝さんぽぽ",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771708277,
      "updated": 1771712068
    },
    {
      "id": "699a30bc0000000000dfa049",
      "text": "  息は白いけど、いい天気で暖かくなりそう。 ",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771712703,
      "updated": 1771712719
    },
    {
      "id": "699a35380000000000dfa04b",
      "text": " おのれ花粉め",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771713847,
      "updated": 1771713888
    },
    {
      "id": "699a875400000000009501a5",
      "text": " [Docker]絡みでなんか動かなかったら、自分ならこう動くかな？と思ったメモ",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1771734868,
      "updated": 1771770656
    },
    {
      "id": "699a880200000000009501b3",
      "text": " \t[2026/02/22#699a8154000000000096a8e3] をみて、自分ならこの辺を見るなぁと思った箇所",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771735043,
      "updated": 1771735063
    },
    {
      "id": "699a878e00000000009501b2",
      "text": " \tどこが調子悪いのかを探すために、色々と試す",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771734926,
      "updated": 1771734940
    },
    {
      "id": "699a883c00000000009501b4",
      "text": " \t\t[/nishio/最新のChromeはHTTPSのページでHTTPの画像表示を許さない] このパターンだったら、以下で問題は起きないはず →Chromeが原因かネットワーク(ホストやDockder)が原因かを切り分ける",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771735101,
      "updated": 1771735187
    },
    {
      "id": "699a877700000000009501a8",
      "text": " \t \tdockerの中でGUIを使えるなら、Docketの中のブラウザで、それぞれのurlを開いてみる",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771734904,
      "updated": 1771735139
    },
    {
      "id": "699a877700000000009501a9",
      "text": " \t \tdockerの動いてるホスト機のブラウザで、それぞれのurlを開いてみる",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771734904,
      "updated": 1771735141
    },
    {
      "id": "699a877700000000009501aa",
      "text": " \t\t 同じネットワーク内のDockerの動いてない別のマシン（スマホとか）のブラウザで、localhost以外のurlを開いてみる",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771734904,
      "updated": 1771735142
    },
    {
      "id": "699a8ac300000000009501b6",
      "text": " \t\t Chromeのネットワークタブで、どんなエラーが出てるのかも一緒に見る",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771735748,
      "updated": 1771735761
    },
    {
      "id": "699a877700000000009501ab",
      "text": "\t 原因がネットワークっぽい場合には、以下が問題になりそう",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771734904,
      "updated": 1771736150
    },
    {
      "id": "699a877700000000009501ac",
      "text": "\t  ホスト側のポート開放不足",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771734904,
      "updated": 1771735331
    },
    {
      "id": "699a877700000000009501ad",
      "text": "\t  ホスト→Dockerのポート転送設定",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771734904,
      "updated": 1771735331
    },
    {
      "id": "699a877700000000009501ae",
      "text": "\t  Docker側での設定不足（ポートが閉じてる、ファイアウォールが動いてる）",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771734904,
      "updated": 1771735331
    },
    {
      "id": "699a877700000000009501af",
      "text": "\t  ホスト側のファイアウォール",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771734904,
      "updated": 1771735331
    },
    {
      "id": "699a877700000000009501b0",
      "text": "\t  (xxxx.localの名前解決の失敗 ←IPでもうまくいかないからちょっと違ってそう)",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771734904,
      "updated": 1771735497
    },
    {
      "id": "699a891e00000000009501b5",
      "text": " \t自分はDocker詳しいわけではないので、問題切り分けしつつ、原因を想像しつつ、あとはLLMに全部放り込んで一緒に調査してもらうかなぁ。",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771735327,
      "updated": 1771735374
    },
    {
      "id": "699a877700000000009501b1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771734904,
      "updated": 1771735039
    },
    {
      "id": "699a260e0000000000b2e836",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1771709967,
      "updated": 1771709969
    },
    {
      "id": "699a26110000000000b2e837",
      "text": " 旅行2日目",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1771709970,
      "updated": 1771709974
    },
    {
      "id": "699a45370000000000d55533",
      "text": " 電波の入らないところが多いなぁ",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1771717944,
      "updated": 1771717952
    },
    {
      "id": "699ac2d60000000000ee8a0b",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/fc3772aeaa5e2e0360d0d003d85e967a]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1771750103,
      "updated": 1771750121
    },
    {
      "id": "699ac2e80000000000ee8a0c",
      "text": "  独特の石",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1771750121,
      "updated": 1771750134
    },
    {
      "id": "699ae369000000000027808b",
      "text": "  ケルンかな[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1771758441,
      "updated": 1771758482
    },
    {
      "id": "699a62fc0000000000110aa1",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/475497a910480f43e0b8f602098bf05e]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1771725565,
      "updated": 1771725583
    },
    {
      "id": "6999c8c50000000000758c05",
      "text": "  富士山を探せ！",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1771686084,
      "updated": 1771725601
    },
    {
      "id": "699ac2290000000000129bba",
      "text": "  いた！[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1771749928,
      "updated": 1771749937
    },
    {
      "id": "699acfb70000000000bce165",
      "text": "  面白い！だまし絵みたいだ[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1771753400,
      "updated": 1771753408
    },
    {
      "id": "699a8c3900000000001b04c8",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/5c9324dde56262cb7030b40e5203f351]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1771736122,
      "updated": 1771736139
    },
    {
      "id": "699ac62200000000008be838",
      "text": " 　具材なんだろう…あおさしか分からない…[nomadoor.icon]",
      "userId": "5f0ae250e8cd56001ee2dacc",
      "created": 1771751124,
      "updated": 1771751133
    },
    {
      "id": "699ac7160000000000ee8a0d",
      "text": " 　お餅、[ムロアジ]のすり身、とのこと[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1771751191,
      "updated": 1771753948
    },
    {
      "id": "699a8c4a00000000001b04c9",
      "text": " 登山で頑張ったのであとはまったり過ごそう",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1771736139,
      "updated": 1771736632
    },
    {
      "id": "699a8e3800000000001b04ca",
      "text": "  5歳の娘も頑張った",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1771736633,
      "updated": 1771736640
    },
    {
      "id": "699a8e3f00000000001b04cb",
      "text": " さて私はどこにいるでしょう？",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1771736640,
      "updated": 1771736646
    },
    {
      "id": "699a91e700000000001b04cc",
      "text": " 空き家は多いが持ち主不明とかでなかなか厳しいらしい",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1771737576,
      "updated": 1771737588
    },
    {
      "id": "699abfdd0000000000ee8a08",
      "text": " 温泉",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1771749343,
      "updated": 1771749345
    },
    {
      "id": "699abfe00000000000ee8a09",
      "text": " 宿に戻る",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1771749345,
      "updated": 1771749350
    },
    {
      "id": "699abfea0000000000ee8a0a",
      "text": "  今日の活動はおしまい、娘は宿でテレビに釘付け",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1771749355,
      "updated": 1771749369
    },
    {
      "id": "699b4ac00000000000220b9d",
      "text": "   旅先のテレビ、つい見てしまう[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1771784897,
      "updated": 1771784917
    },
    {
      "id": "699a63160000000000110aa3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1771725591,
      "updated": 1771725591
    },
    {
      "id": "699a63160000000000110aa4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1771725591,
      "updated": 1771725591
    },
    {
      "id": "699a49e800000000000552fa",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771719145,
      "updated": 1771719147
    },
    {
      "id": "699a49eb00000000000552fb",
      "text": "　9時",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771719148,
      "updated": 1771719151
    },
    {
      "id": "699ab39a00000000000f4287",
      "text": "　[クレアチン]の話がタイムラインに流れてくる、少し気になる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771746202,
      "updated": 1771746679
    },
    {
      "id": "699ab57700000000000f4288",
      "text": "\t何にでも関係を見出す陰謀論者、いまだに僕も安野さんも未踏出身ということには気づいてないみたい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771746680,
      "updated": 1771746812
    },
    {
      "id": "699ab5fc00000000000f4289",
      "text": "\t\t「裏の勢力に牛耳られている！」とかいいやすいのにな(なんせ修了生が4桁いるからw)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771746813,
      "updated": 1771749447
    },
    {
      "id": "699ab61d00000000000f428a",
      "text": "  未踏が裏勢力扱いされるようになったらウケる[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1771746845,
      "updated": 1771747223
    },
    {
      "id": "699ab79700000000006b0a71",
      "text": "  　そういえばscrapboxの開発者も未踏出身……全部未踏の仕業だ！()",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1771747223,
      "updated": 1771747277
    },
    {
      "id": "699ac32c0000000000a1ff49",
      "text": "  どういう[陰謀論]なんですか？ [suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1771750189,
      "updated": 1771750221
    },
    {
      "id": "699ab61d00000000000f428b",
      "text": "　　　今のところ「チームみらいが推してるプルラリティのウェブサイトを作ってるのはサイボウズ！サイボウズの西尾はチームみらいを応援するような発言もしてる！」とか言ってる[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771746845,
      "updated": 1771750798
    },
    {
      "id": "699ac52000000000001d6480",
      "text": "　　　「それが何か？」という気持ち",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771750688,
      "updated": 1771750708
    },
    {
      "id": "699ac53400000000001d6481",
      "text": "　　　彼らの中ではなんらかの隠されている秘密を暴いた気持ちになってるみたいw",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771750708,
      "updated": 1771750877
    },
    {
      "id": "699ac8270000000000a1ff4a",
      "text": "　　　 [公開情報]ですよね、それ [suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1771751464,
      "updated": 1771751493
    },
    {
      "id": "699ae38600000000001d6487",
      "text": "　　　 yes[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771758474,
      "updated": 1771758477
    },
    {
      "id": "699ae38d00000000001d6488",
      "text": "　　　 　そもそもなんら特殊な情報獲得手段を持ってるわけでもない一般人がネットで検索して発見できる情報は全て公開情報なので陰謀の発見などできてないのだが、自分は世界の真理に気付いたと思っているようだ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771758478,
      "updated": 1771758576
    },
    {
      "id": "699a49f000000000000552fc",
      "text": "\t[ANLIFE]買った！",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771719152,
      "updated": 1771751067
    },
    {
      "id": "699ae32800000000001d6482",
      "text": "\t　惑星サイズ最大になった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771758376,
      "updated": 1771758384
    },
    {
      "id": "699af3d500000000001d6489",
      "text": "\t　テックツリーを全て解放した",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771762646,
      "updated": 1771762654
    },
    {
      "id": "699af3de00000000001d648a",
      "text": "\t　なかなか空中ユニットに進化しない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771762655,
      "updated": 1771762676
    },
    {
      "id": "699af92d00000000007aa7a1",
      "text": "\t　やりたい[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1771764013,
      "updated": 1771764016
    },
    {
      "id": "699ac69b00000000000f428c",
      "text": "\thttps://x.com/motcho_tw/status/2025480605048471692?s=46&t=gkSZtjGEtUZPO0JCzBxCBw",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771751067,
      "updated": 1771758387
    },
    {
      "id": "699ae33300000000001d6483",
      "text": "\t　わかるー",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771758388,
      "updated": 1771758392
    },
    {
      "id": "699ae33700000000001d6484",
      "text": "\t　こういうときにCosenseは最適",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771758392,
      "updated": 1771758401
    },
    {
      "id": "699ae34100000000001d6485",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771758401,
      "updated": 1771758401
    },
    {
      "id": "699ae34100000000001d6486",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771758401,
      "updated": 1771758401
    },
    {
      "id": "699a51040000000000434e7c",
      "text": "[hoagecko.icon]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1771720965,
      "updated": 1771720965
    },
    {
      "id": "699a51060000000000434e7d",
      "text": " 一昨日([2026/02/20])に買ったレコードのメターデータの入力が終わった",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1771720966,
      "updated": 1771720994
    },
    {
      "id": "699a534c0000000000434e7e",
      "text": " \t面倒だったが満足",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1771721549,
      "updated": 1771721862
    },
    {
      "id": "699a537e0000000000434e80",
      "text": " 解説で大好きな音楽家の知らない話が読めた",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1771721598,
      "updated": 1771721868
    },
    {
      "id": "699a548b0000000000434e82",
      "text": "  ほとんどこれを目当てに買った",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1771721868,
      "updated": 1771721916
    },
    {
      "id": "699a54ba0000000000434e83",
      "text": "  知らない写真が見れたこともありがたい",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1771721916,
      "updated": 1771721916
    },
    {
      "id": "699a49f000000000000552fd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771719152,
      "updated": 1771719152
    },
    {
      "id": "699a594f00000000001adf37",
      "text": "[W7kA9pX2.icon]",
      "userId": "644fa04c7142e4001b4b5d09",
      "created": 1771723087,
      "updated": 1771723089
    },
    {
      "id": "699a595100000000001adf39",
      "text": "　[ポンカン]が安かったので買った　おいしい",
      "userId": "644fa04c7142e4001b4b5d09",
      "created": 1771723089,
      "updated": 1771723107
    },
    {
      "id": "699a596300000000001adf3a",
      "text": "　　みかんのように簡単に手で剥ける手軽さがいい",
      "userId": "644fa04c7142e4001b4b5d09",
      "created": 1771723107,
      "updated": 1771723130
    },
    {
      "id": "699a597100000000001adf3b",
      "text": "　　みかんより若干皮が硬くて身もサクサクしてて酸味が強くさわやかな味わい",
      "userId": "644fa04c7142e4001b4b5d09",
      "created": 1771723121,
      "updated": 1771723166
    },
    {
      "id": "699a59c400000000001adf3c",
      "text": "　　　みかんばかり食べがちなので味変になってそこも良い",
      "userId": "644fa04c7142e4001b4b5d09",
      "created": 1771723204,
      "updated": 1771723222
    },
    {
      "id": "699a5ce50000000000955c3a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771724005,
      "updated": 1771724005
    },
    {
      "id": "699a5c250000000000955c37",
      "text": "[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771723813,
      "updated": 1771724010
    },
    {
      "id": "699a5ce90000000000955c3b",
      "text": " 自分も昨日[ポンカン]を食べた",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771724010,
      "updated": 1771724022
    },
    {
      "id": "699a5c2b0000000000955c38",
      "text": "  味が強くて美味しかった",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771723819,
      "updated": 1771724024
    },
    {
      "id": "699a5cde0000000000955c39",
      "text": "  みかんのポジションを奪取できそう",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1771723999,
      "updated": 1771724044
    },
    {
      "id": "699a6c5200000000004ba94d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1771727955,
      "updated": 1771727955
    },
    {
      "id": "699a6c5200000000004ba94e",
      "text": "[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1771727955,
      "updated": 1771727956
    },
    {
      "id": "699a6c5400000000004ba94f",
      "text": "　12時間寝たまずい",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1771727957,
      "updated": 1771727961
    },
    {
      "id": "699a594f00000000001adf38",
      "text": " さらに1時間寝た",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1771723087,
      "updated": 1771748945
    },
    {
      "id": "699abe4a0000000000521da1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1771748938,
      "updated": 1771748938
    },
    {
      "id": "699a6da00000000000d75766",
      "text": "[nyarla.icon]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1771728289,
      "updated": 1771728291
    },
    {
      "id": "699a6da30000000000d75768",
      "text": "\t午前中はごろごろしていた",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1771728291,
      "updated": 1771728297
    },
    {
      "id": "699a6ddd0000000000d75769",
      "text": "\tブラウザのタブが[あとで読む]代わりになっているため、170ページを超えるタブが開かれている",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1771728349,
      "updated": 1771728391
    },
    {
      "id": "699a6e070000000000d7576a",
      "text": "\t\tいいかげん減らしたい",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1771728392,
      "updated": 1771728397
    },
    {
      "id": "699a75ea00000000001f95c4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1771730411,
      "updated": 1771730411
    },
    {
      "id": "699a75eb00000000001f95c5",
      "text": "[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1771730411,
      "updated": 1771730412
    },
    {
      "id": "699a75ec00000000001f95c6",
      "text": "\t朝から、ず が つう である。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1771730412,
      "updated": 1771730422
    },
    {
      "id": "699a6da00000000000d75767",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1771728289,
      "updated": 1771728290
    },
    {
      "id": "699a7c2f0000000000f36f60",
      "text": "[mtane0412.icon]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1771732015,
      "updated": 1771732015
    },
    {
      "id": "699a7c2f0000000000f36f61",
      "text": " マリオテニス、ドンキーだらけで勝てなくなってきたので自分もドンキーになったら勝率9割になってA+になった",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1771732015,
      "updated": 1771732036
    },
    {
      "id": "699a7c430000000000f36f62",
      "text": "  こうして[みんなドンキーになっていく]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1771732036,
      "updated": 1771735198
    },
    {
      "id": "699a7c5c0000000000f36f63",
      "text": "  [フィーバーラケット]ありでバランス調整されているのでフィーバーなし条件だとドンキーに弱点がなくなるのだと思う",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1771732062,
      "updated": 1771735215
    },
    {
      "id": "699a7c750000000000f36f64",
      "text": "   パワーとスピードがあって身体がデカいのでボールに手が届いてパワー系なのでトップスピンもフラットも強く、特殊能力でスライスも重い",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1771732085,
      "updated": 1771732119
    },
    {
      "id": "699a7ca50000000000f36f65",
      "text": "  フィーバーありなしだけでなくドンキーありなしが必要なくらいには壊れてそうに見える",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1771732133,
      "updated": 1771732156
    },
    {
      "id": "699a7cbc0000000000f36f66",
      "text": "  テニスゲームのバランス調整は難しそうだなと思った",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1771732157,
      "updated": 1771732163
    },
    {
      "id": "699af584000000000023e871",
      "text": "  S-になった",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1771763077,
      "updated": 1771763081
    },
    {
      "id": "699a7c2e0000000000f36f5f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1771732014,
      "updated": 1771732014
    },
    {
      "id": "699a7cf20000000000d6600b",
      "text": "[nomadoor.icon]",
      "userId": "5f0ae250e8cd56001ee2dacc",
      "created": 1771732387,
      "updated": 1771732387
    },
    {
      "id": "699a7cf30000000000d6600c",
      "text": " 全てが綺麗に収まるUI設計が出来て全く実装に進んでいないのに悦に入っている",
      "userId": "5f0ae250e8cd56001ee2dacc",
      "created": 1771732388,
      "updated": 1771732424
    },
    {
      "id": "699db5a10000000000d1beab",
      "text": "  こういう時が一番楽しい[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "59fb21121207900012774b17",
      "created": 1771943329,
      "updated": 1771943333
    },
    {
      "id": "699a7cf30000000000d6600d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f0ae250e8cd56001ee2dacc",
      "created": 1771732388,
      "updated": 1771732388
    },
    {
      "id": "699a8152000000000096a8e2",
      "text": "[koyoshi.icon]",
      "userId": "6606ca1148e7150024f0f07d",
      "created": 1771733331,
      "updated": 1771733332
    },
    {
      "id": "699a8154000000000096a8e3",
      "text": " ローカルのDockerでWebサーバを立ち上げ、Cosenseに以下のように書くと`localhost`で指定した時しか表示できない。なぜだろう？",
      "userId": "6606ca1148e7150024f0f07d",
      "created": 1771733333,
      "updated": 1771733335
    },
    {
      "id": "699a8157000000000096a8e4",
      "text": "  `[http://localhost:8000/apache-docker.png]`",
      "userId": "6606ca1148e7150024f0f07d",
      "created": 1771733335,
      "updated": 1771733335
    },
    {
      "id": "699a8157000000000096a8e5",
      "text": "  `[http://wasabi.local:8000/apache-docker.png]`",
      "userId": "6606ca1148e7150024f0f07d",
      "created": 1771733335,
      "updated": 1771733335
    },
    {
      "id": "699a8157000000000096a8e6",
      "text": "  `[http://<IPアドレス>:8000/apache-docker.png]`",
      "userId": "6606ca1148e7150024f0f07d",
      "created": 1771733335,
      "updated": 1771733335
    },
    {
      "id": "699a8150000000000096a8e1",
      "text": "\t\tこれとか？ [/nishio/最新のChromeはHTTPSのページでHTTPの画像表示を許さない][nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771733329,
      "updated": 1771733920
    },
    {
      "id": "699a839f00000000000f4285",
      "text": "\t\t\tで、localhostだけ何らかの方法で許可されてるとか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771733920,
      "updated": 1771733935
    },
    {
      "id": "699a89d00000000000f3748a",
      "text": "\t\t\tChromeを使ってるけど、それぞれのURLをブラウザに直接貼ると どれも表示できるので、Cosenseの問題かなと思ってみた[koyoshi.icon]",
      "userId": "6606ca1148e7150024f0f07d",
      "created": 1771735504,
      "updated": 1771735581
    },
    {
      "id": "699a928500000000009db55e",
      "text": "\t\t[nishio.icon]さんの関連ページ見ててなんとなく理解した",
      "userId": "6606ca1148e7150024f0f07d",
      "created": 1771737733,
      "updated": 1771737766
    },
    {
      "id": "699a92ac00000000009db55f",
      "text": " \t\tどうやらHTTPS化しないといけないようだ",
      "userId": "6606ca1148e7150024f0f07d",
      "created": 1771737772,
      "updated": 1771737821
    },
    {
      "id": "699a84000000000000983202",
      "text": "\t\t[2026/02/22#699a875400000000009501a5] こんな時に自分ならどうするかな？と思ったメモ書き[taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1771734016,
      "updated": 1771735010
    },
    {
      "id": "699ab45e000000000030e29e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1771746399,
      "updated": 1771746399
    },
    {
      "id": "699ab45e000000000030e29f",
      "text": "[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1771746399,
      "updated": 1771746400
    },
    {
      "id": "699ab45f000000000030e2a0",
      "text": " ぐったり",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1771746400,
      "updated": 1771746403
    },
    {
      "id": "699ab462000000000030e2a1",
      "text": " 明日は大学行きたい",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1771746403,
      "updated": 1771746405
    },
    {
      "id": "699ab80100000000006b0a72",
      "text": " クロスカントリー見た",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1771747330,
      "updated": 1771747337
    },
    {
      "id": "699aee9f00000000002e2335",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771761312,
      "updated": 1771761312
    },
    {
      "id": "699aeea000000000002e2336",
      "text": "[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771761313,
      "updated": 1771761315
    },
    {
      "id": "699aeea300000000002e2337",
      "text": " 花粉症の薬を飲まずに外出してしまった",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771761315,
      "updated": 1771761343
    },
    {
      "id": "699aeec900000000002e2338",
      "text": "  目がぁ",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771761353,
      "updated": 1771761359
    },
    {
      "id": "699b0ef000000000002d4c89",
      "text": "   目がぁ",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771769585,
      "updated": 1771769591
    },
    {
      "id": "699b0ef800000000002d4c8a",
      "text": " いちごを食べた",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1771769592,
      "updated": 1771769689
    },
    {
      "id": "699a83af00000000000f4286",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1771733936,
      "updated": 1771733937
    },
    {
      "id": "6999c8b97838e30000006a21b1",
      "text": "[2026/02/21]←2026/02/22→[2026/02/23]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1771686071,
      "updated": 1771686071
    },
    {
      "id": "6999c8b97838e3000000d88dbd",
      "text": "[/ [2026/02.icon]]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1771686071,
      "updated": 1771686071
    }
  ]
}